{"date":"2001-07-04","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/45/0a/10276_ys05r.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/45/0a/10276_ys05r.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/45/0a/10276_ys05r.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/45/0a/10276_ys05r.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/45/0a/10276_ys05r.jpg"},"summary":"事情起源于六年前。大地隆起，日本的神奈川县在分离之后就被孤立。以后在神奈川出生的少数人就懂得运用阿尔达超能力。阿尔达超能力是一种能够将物质分解再构成的力量…… \r\n　　数马和刘鳯是对立的，因为所属的地方不同。数马是一个为了钱而生活的人，以自己的超能力来为自己获得金钱，从而满足自己的生活。刘鳯是一个为了找寻阿尔达结晶体，为自己的妈妈报仇而加入圣堂/神圣部队（HOLY）的人。圣堂是由阿尔达超能力者组成的警察部队，为了保护没有超能力者、制止超能力犯罪而设立，所以圣堂的人会捕捉周围土生的超能力者。该日数马和刘鳯的相见就是因为圣堂的一次行动而促成…….......","name":"スクライド","name_cn":"分身战士","tags":[{"name":"SUNRISE","count":156,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":126,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2001","count":109,"total_cont":0},{"name":"谷口悟朗","count":105,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":81,"total_cont":0},{"name":"平井久司","count":72,"total_cont":0},{"name":"黑田洋介","count":52,"total_cont":0},{"name":"热血","count":44,"total_cont":0},{"name":"分身战士","count":41,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科幻","count":29,"total_cont":0},{"name":"超能力","count":26,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":23,"total_cont":0},{"name":"黒田洋介","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"谷口悟郎","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"保志総一朗","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2001年7月","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVA","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"保志总一朗","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000s","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"サンライズ","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧情","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中川幸太郎","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2001夏","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"绿川光","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"田村由香里","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"緑川光","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SF","count":2,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value"